casebody.data:
Monday, March 25, 1996

MOTION DOCKET

95-1703. Nehls v. Quad K Advertising.

Cuyahoga County, No. 67358. This cause is here on appeal from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County. Upon consideration of the joint motion to stay further proceedings pending a ruling on the joint motion to remand appeal to implement settlement,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion to stay further proceedings be, and hereby is, granted.
